'''伊斯蘭前進軍–自由敘利亞軍衝突'''是從2013年12月6日起進行的戰鬥，同屬[[敘利亞反對派|敘利亞反對派]]的[[伊斯蘭前進軍_(敘利亞)|伊斯蘭前進軍]]（Islamic Front）和[[自由敘利亞軍|自由敘利亞軍]]爆發軍事衝突。

伊斯蘭前進軍（the Islamic Fornt）又可譯為伊斯蘭陣線。背後有土耳其及卡達的支持。

== 背景 ==
伊斯蘭前進軍於2013年11月22日成立，共由七個民兵組織組成，屬於敘利亞反對派的部隊之一<ref name="AJE22Nov">{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/11/major-syrian-rebel-groups-join-forces-20131122141129975421.html|title=Major Syrian rebel groups join forces|publisher=[[半島電視台|半島電視台]]|last=Atassi|first=Basma|date=2013-11-22|accessdate=2013-12-10|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611183859/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/11/major-syrian-rebel-groups-join-forces-20131122141129975421.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月，伊斯蘭前進軍宣布拒絕聽從自由敘利亞軍的指揮<ref name="telegraph5dec">{{Cite news|title=Leading Syrian rebels defect, dealing blow to fight against al-Qaeda|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/10498477/Leading-Syrian-rebels-defect-dealing-blow-to-fight-against-al-Qaeda.html|work=Daily Telegraph|date=2013-12-05|accessdate=2013-12-10|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613090121/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/10498477/Leading-Syrian-rebels-defect-dealing-blow-to-fight-against-al-Qaeda.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 攻占巴艾哈瓦基地 ==
12月7日，自由敘利亞軍（FSA）發言人Louay Meqdad表示前晚伊斯蘭前進軍闖入了敘土邊境的巴艾哈瓦（Bab al-Hawa），雖然FSA試圖撫平衝突，但是伊斯蘭前進軍要求FSA立即撤出基地，並將旗幟換成該團體旗幟，同時也奪取了FSA從[[土耳其|土耳其]]帶來的武器<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.digitaljournal.com/article/363536|title=Syria: Islamic Front fighters seize bases belonging to FSA rebels|agency=Digital Journal|date=2013-12-07|accessdate=2013-12-10|archive-date=2018-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180928060923/http://www.digitaljournal.com/article/363536|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據報導衝突中至少五人陣亡<ref name="7DecReuters">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/07/us-syria-crisis-fsa-idUSBRE9B607S20131207|title=Syrian Islamists seize Western-backed rebel bases: monitoring group|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2013-12-07|accessdate=2013-12-10|first1=Alexander|last1=Dziadosz|first2=Dasha|last2=Afanasieva|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924191512/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/07/us-syria-crisis-fsa-idUSBRE9B607S20131207|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

12月10日，伊斯蘭前進軍包圍了{{link-en|巴艾哈瓦邊境管制站|Bab al-Hawa Border Crossing}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Dec-10/240625-syria-islamists-seize-turkey-border-crossing-monitor.ashx|title=Syria Islamists seize Turkey border crossing: monitor|publisher=The Daily Star|date=2013-12-10|accessdate=2013-12-10|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929090840/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Dec-10/240625-syria-islamists-seize-turkey-border-crossing-monitor.ashx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩天後，有消息傳出由於戰況不利，FSA最高指揮官{{link-en|薩利姆·伊德里斯|Salim Idris}}離開當地指揮中心抵達[[卡達|卡達]][[多哈|多哈]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/business/wall-street-journal/islamists-drive-out-usbacked-syrian-rebel-general-salim-idris/story-fnay3ubk-1226781918266#mm-premium|title=Islamists drive out US-backed Syrian rebel general Salim Idris|publisher=[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]|date=2013-12-13|accessdate=2013-12-13|archive-date=2013-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215144317/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/business/wall-street-journal/islamists-drive-out-usbacked-syrian-rebel-general-salim-idris/story-fnay3ubk-1226781918266#mm-premium|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，FSA否認了此消息，並表示伊斯蘭前進軍已被命令前往看守為對抗[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]所使用的倉庫<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/1.563189|title=Syrian rebels deny reports top commander forced to flee|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2013-12-12|accessdate=2013-12-12|archive-date=2015-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713193129/http://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/1.563189|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

